Changes by ngdeleito (see git history for the full details)

2012-09-01 onwards
- changed version number to 4.4
- unpacked and removed easygestures.jar file
- reindented source code in several files
- rewrote deprecated versions of setTimeout() function calls
- made several changes in the preferences dialog, among which:
-- removed support for multiple skins
-- removed popup menu to change language
-- split the "Behavior" pane in two
-- made use of XUL's preferences system
- fixed some warnings
- removed popup for nextTab, prevTab and undoCloseTab actions
- removed input box for entering URLs
- removed linear menu
- removed Translate/Explain action
- changed behaviour of Search Web action, which now uses Firefox's search engines
- changed behaviour of Highlight/Clear action so that it now toggles Firefox's find bar
- renamed highlight action to toggleFindBar
- changed behaviour of Daily Readings action:
-- it does no longer provide default bookmarks upon creation of the daily readings folder
-- it now opens all bookmarks in new tabs
- removed red tag for links
- made select boxes for actions non editable
- removed runProgramFile actions
- removed custom about dialog
- added new Restart Firefox action
- easyGestures is now a restartless extension
- removed welcome page
- renamed and adapted accordingly privateBrowsing action to newPrivateWindow
- renamed closeBrowser action to quit
- removed statusbar icon
- removed mail action
- added focusLocationBar action
- removed ability to open menu only on drag
- removed the omit tooltips delay option
- removed support for upgrading from versions prior to 4.3.2
- moved preferences to the extensions. branch
- removed properties action
- removed sendLink action
